[h4 id=DailyPolarium 
	"Daily Polarium
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"On this mode you casually need to finish all 365 puzzles per day (a year)..
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"You will be asked to enter in the date you want your game to start at. the date selection can go up from January 1, 2000 to December 31, 2099. Once you select the date, you'll have to complete in one year (or 
	[a href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leap_year rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"366 days depending on the year
	]a
	". For example if you started the game in 2008, that would an extended year by one day).
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Daily Polarium puzzles are pre-determined: 
	$LF
